{"tid":1064612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【台立委補選】「韓流」失效未能保2席 國民黨怪中間選民沒投票","createTime":"2019-03-16T16:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T08:04:54.000Z","uid":144372,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"62a0db547cf0f3399c4aa7ea51dd64c40aae3c9e","tid":1064612,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59376684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59376684&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=5a7c5ec1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59376684&h=3421956a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59376684</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣今日舉行立委補選，選出4名立委，原以為靠着高雄市長韓國瑜的「韓流」拉票，可以「守二搶二」的國民黨，卻在4席中只得1席。國民黨發言人歐陽龍承認「補選結果不如預期」，但他埋怨是中間選民未有出來投票，無法改變基本支持不及民進黨的形勢。"},{"pid":"18efe019450c301630c90895b289f90d49a3651c","tid":1064612,"uid":144372,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"歐陽龍在選舉有結果後舉行記者會，他表示原來的評估，是投票率有45%，便能夠改變基本支持不足的形勢，可是，「中間選民沒有站出來投票」，令到出現這個結果。<br />\n<br />\n分別奪得新北、台南議席的民進黨，秘書長羅文嘉認為選舉結果顯示民進黨沒有贏，「只是止血而已」，他認為投票給民進黨的選民，是期望民進黨「堅守台灣民主價值，堅定站在台灣立場，守住世代民主生活方式」，他認為未來1年多，民進黨內要更緊密團結，才可以克服所有「外在困難」，才真正守衞民主自由價值跟制度。"},{"pid":"04c0fce9c9ffb2277d35620eee7f438d27d3a49c","tid":1064612,"uid":21545,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"露出馬腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學人屌票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d9b03079ab31b42e1d5d57a940c3ba16ab58c8","tid":1064612,"uid":36551,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"露晒底啦吹水佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"